<div id="pf9c5" class="pf w16 h124" data-page-no="9c5"><div class="pc pc9c5 w16 h124"><div class="t md03 xa h18d y219b ff1 fs1d fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">AN OPINION </div><div class="t m5f9 x3f h27 y1bf2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Uncle Ben&apos;s Cobblestones&quot; beautifully de-</div><div class="t m3f2 x4e h27 y1ed8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">monstrates in one brief, unique little volume, how </div><div class="t m16b x4e h27 y10c8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the &quot;common things&quot; of life may become more </div><div class="t m7e7 x4e h27 y19b3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">useful than even acres of *diamonds; for after all </div><div class="t m4da x4e h27 y18c3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is said and done, it is the ability to use a thing </div><div class="t m1c8 x4e h27 y17b3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that makes it of real worth to us. Uncle Ben&apos;s </div><div class="t ma7d x4e h27 y1bcc ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whole purpose seems to point to &quot;wealth of </div><div class="t m649 x4e h27 y158d ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">character&quot; and real &quot;soul culture.&quot; </div><div class="t m1289 x50 h27 y142a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">There is a ray of sunshine streaming through-</div><div class="t m602 x4e h27 y1d01 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">out the entire volume. At the same time there is </div><div class="t m3c9 x4e h27 y1ef1 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a staid sobriety of good cheer that never once </div><div class="t m134c x4e h27 y1c5f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">touches the fickle so prevalent in books written </div><div class="t mf5e x4e h27 y6ac ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the children of our day. Observation and </div><div class="t m6e3 x4e h27 y1101 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">application are two of the greatest features in </div><div class="t m5e8 x4e h27 y194c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">character-building. Uncle Ben seems to know </div><div class="t m1223 x4e h27 y2155 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what he is talking about along these lines. </div><div class="t m6c5 x4e h27 y1b90 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These two lessons are taught on every page in the </div><div class="t m1ff x4e h27 y1b18 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">book. No child can escape their meaning. And </div><div class="t m10f x4e h27 y1c00 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with these lessons there is a moral fragrance that </div><div class="t m198 x4e h27 y648 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">can not fail to please every true parent. The </div><div class="t m223 x4e h27 y17c1 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spirit of the book is good for the older children. </div><div class="t m3ef x4e h27 y14ce ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It makes one feel as though he would like to live </div><div class="t m6a3 x4e h27 y1da9 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a century, do good, and grow old gracefully. </div><div class="t mdf5 x5a h27 y1bea ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">W. H. COVELL. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
